<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((الروض النضير)</span>) <span class="c2">(٦٩٩)</span> , <span class="c2">((ظلال الجنة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٩١٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>